thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Rick Kirk

author: Rick Kirk
title: Rick Kirk
text: Can't fault these guys. The actually get it and provide you, the customer, with service! Congrats to StoreDJ. My recent purchase had to come from an interstate warehouse so they auto upgraded me to next day delivery and contacted me to let me know. Can't fault their speed, communicatons or effort. I'd recommend them to everyone.
